						<summary>

						<p>Registers a gift of land by purchase, by <hi rend="bold">Viṭṭaya,</hi> a <hi rend="italic">Sēṉaibōya</hi> of <hi rend="italic">Mahāpradhāni Sandhivigrahi</hi> <hi rend="bold">Bhīmaṇṇa-Daṇḍanāyaka,</hi> a member of <hi rend="italic">Śrīkaraṇam</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Sōmēśvaradēva,</hi> for the supply of garlands to the god Aḻagiyamaṇavāḷa-Perumāḷ. The record is dated in the <hi rend="bold">24th year</hi> of the king's reign.</p>						

						</summary>
